<p style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: #666666;">Remember that you don&rsquo;t have to sell solar &ndash; just provide referrals! It takes only minutes of conversation with a customer to get them excited about going solar.</p>
<p style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: #666666;">If 2 team members refer 5 sales each you could put $9,000 in your pocket*<br /><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; color: #666666;"><span style="font-size: 11px;"><em>*based on $150 per qualified lead and $750 per sale</em></span></span></p>
